text: Nadiya Bychkova (Ukrainian: Надия Бычкова) (born 24 August 1989) is a Ukrainian ballroom and Latin American dancer. She is a multiple Slovenian ballroom and Latin American dance champion, as well as a two-time World and European champion in 10 dances. In 2017, she joined as a professional dancer on the BBC One celebrity dancing show Strictly Come Dancing. Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Dancers
